<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>✅ 訊息已送出</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .success-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            animation: bounceIn 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }

        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: scale(1.2);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        .success-icon svg {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            color: white;
        }

        .checkmark {
            stroke-dasharray: 100;
            stroke-dashoffset: 100;
            animation: draw 0.6s ease-out 0.5s forwards;
        }

        @keyframes draw {
            to {
                stroke-dashoffset: 0;
            }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #047857;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #065f46;
            width: 80px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .info-value {
            color: #047857;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        .message-preview {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #d1fae5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            color: #334155;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            max-height: 100px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        }

        .footer-text {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .service-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .service-badge.free {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .success-card {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .success-icon {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
            }

            .success-icon svg {
                width: 40px;
                height: 40px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="success-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline class="checkmark" points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>訊息已成功送出！</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">感謝您的聯繫，我們會盡快回覆您。</p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">姓名</span>
                <span class="info-value">
                    <%= contact.name %>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">Email</span>
                <span class="info-value">
                    <%= contact.email %>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="info-label">服務</span>
                <span class="info-value">
                    <span class="service-badge <%= contact.servicePrice === 0 ? 'free' : '' %>">
                        <%= contact.service || 'General Inquiry' %>
                    </span>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row" style="flex-direction: column;">
                <span class="info-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">訊息內容</span>
                <div class="message-preview">
                    <%= contact.message %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="http://localhost:5173" class="back-btn">
            ← 返回首頁
        </a>

        <p class="footer-text">
            提交時間：<%= new Date(contact.createdAt).toLocaleString('zh-TW') %>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>